title: Frida Kahlo Eyeglass Case with Cloth
description:
Known for her self-portraits and bright, bold blooms, this hard shell eyeglass case celebrates Frida Kahlo’s (Mexico, 1907-1954) signature style. The attention grabbing print will ensure you never loose sight of your specs. Includes a matching microfiber lens cloth.

6 ¼ x 2 ½ x 1 ½ in.
